-- Gold Equities to Outperform the Metal, Tocqueville Says
-- B y   D e b a r a t i   R o y
-- 2012-04-13T19:39:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-13/gold-equities-to-outperform-the-metal-tocqueville-says.html
Shares of gold-mining  companies 
will outperform the price of the metal over the next 12 months,
Douglas Groh, who helps manage $10 billion at Tocqueville Asset
Management LP, said today at a conference in  New York . Rising
gold prices will boost the cash flow of producers, he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
